-<sect2 id="keynav-32">
-<title>To Navigate Sliders</title>
-<indexterm>
-<primary>keyboard shortcuts</primary>
-<secondary>for sliders</secondary>
-</indexterm>
-<para>A slider is a control that you use to set a value in a continuous
